include icons.pug

.flex.flex-col.items-start(class='gap-6 py-4')
  span.inline-flex.items-center.justify-center.rounded-full.border.border-primary(class='h-12 w-12 bg-primary/10 text-primary')
    +icon('check', 'h-5 w-5')
  h3.font-serif.text-foreground(class='text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-[-0.02em] leading-tight')
    | Got it.
    |
    span.serif-italic.text-muted-foreground Talk soon.
  p.text-muted-foreground(class='max-w-md text-base leading-relaxed')
    | Thanks for the note. I read every message myself, so the reply will come from
    | me, not a template. Usually within a day, sometimes faster.
  button.inline-flex.items-center.text-foreground.transition-colors(
    type='button'
    data-contact-reset
    class='gap-2 text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary mt-2'
  )
    span Send another
    +icon('arrow-up-right', 'h-3.5 w-3.5')
